{"tid":2153201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳州三隻留學小粉紅違宵禁令, 拍片show off引當地華人譴責","createTime":"2020-08-12T11:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T11:35:53.000Z","uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d95ba6791b75be18b58626f8a58ec3fc35a2de09","tid":2153201,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_FvpC8VhinQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_FvpC8VhinQ&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7QbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=c80efcb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_FvpC8VhinQ</a><br />\n<br />\n【環球薈報】墨爾本留學生違宵禁令惹當地華人譴責<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401463&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401463%26refer%3DShare&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7QbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f7dd3698\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401463%26refer%3DShare&h=ef536233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401463&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，三名中國留學生近日在明知的情況下，違反墨爾本的宵禁令，前往附近的大型連鎖快餐店麥當勞買東西吃，兼且拍片上載到社交網站分享，惹來當地華人的譴責。<br />\n<br />\n這條名為「深夜麥當勞」的短片是在周日凌晨拍攝，片中三人明知故犯，在宵禁令生效期間外出買外賣，甚至認為墨爾本的封城措施等於「放屁」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事留學生在一片謾罵聲中連發兩份聲明道歉，說做錯事不能挽回，他們接受所有批評，又承認態度輕浮，所謂的「勇敢」在法律面前顯得非常幼稚。"}]}